FBIS4-40301 "drsov116_c_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-116 Daily Report 15 Jun 1994 Federal Assembly Law Protecting Law Enforcement Bodies Adopted Law Protecting Law Enforcement Bodies Adopted LD1506204894 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1600 GMT 15 Jun 94 LD1506204894 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Russian BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Vladimir Taranov] [Text] Moscow, 15 Jun -- The State Duma today adopted at its second reading the federal law "On State Protection for Judges, Officials, and Bodies of Law Enforcement and Control." The law ensures protection for judges, officials, and bodies of law enforcement and control whose functions may put their safety in peril. Viktor Mironov, deputy chairman of the State Duma Committee for Security, who presented the law to the deputies, expressed the hope that "this law will make it possible for staff of the law enforcement bodies to start combating crime in earnest."
